Package com.rotartsi.jgame.util

Class ResourceManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.rotartsi.jgame.util.ResourceManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ImageManager, SoundManager
    public abstract class ResourceManager
extends Object
    The framework for resource manager. Implements recursively adding files from a directory.

      • getId

        public String getId​(File file,
                    int baseLen,
                    boolean stripNumbers)
        Derive an ID from a filename and prefix length.
        Parameters:
        file - File to get
        baseLen - length of prefix
        stripNumbers - Whether or not the numbers are stripped from the ID. Useful for random sound playing. For example: we could have hurt1.wav and hurt2.wav use the same id ("hurt") so a random one plays when we call play("hurt"). See SoundManager.
        Returns:
        identifier
